    <item>
      <title>据美联社报道，杀害三人的校园枪击案凶手是内华达大学拉斯维加斯分校的教授</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2023-12-07/vegas-shooter-who-killed-3-was-a-professor-who-recently-applied-for-a-job-at-unlv-ap-source-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[拉斯维加斯（美联社）——当一名枪手在内华达大学拉斯维加斯分校大楼的地板上徘徊时，惊恐的学生和教授们躲在教室和宿舍里，造成三人死亡，第四人重伤，然后在与警方的枪战中死亡。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2023-12-07/vegas-shooter-who-killed-3-was-a-professor-who-recently-applied-for-a-job-at-unlv-ap-source-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 07 Dec 2023 05:30:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>共和党主要人士抨击中国科技贸易限制执法不严</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-07/key-republican-slams-lax-enforcement-of-china-tech-trade-curbs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一位重要的共和党人正在攻击商务部，认为其优先考虑与中国的贸易，而不是严格执行旨在遏制其地缘政治竞争对手的出口管制，从而损害了国家安全。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-07/key-republican-slams-lax-enforcement-of-china-tech-trade-curbs</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 07 Dec 2023 05:01:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>习近平告诉欧盟领导人中国希望成为贸易“关键伙伴”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-07/xi-tells-eu-leaders-the-two-sides-must-work-on-political-trust</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国国家主席习近平在北京会面解决一系列经济问题和不满之际，向欧盟领导人表示，他希望双方成为能够在供应链上建立信任的主要贸易伙伴。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-07/xi-tells-eu-leaders-the-two-sides-must-work-on-political-trust</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 07 Dec 2023 04:40:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国对中国军舰罕见停靠柬埔寨表示担忧</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-07/us-raises-concern-about-chinese-warships-rare-stop-in-cambodia</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在中国军舰罕见访问柬埔寨后，美国呼吁提供有关柬埔寨海军基地的更多信息，再次引发人们对北京希望在这个东南亚国家建立军事设施的担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-07/us-raises-concern-about-chinese-warships-rare-stop-in-cambodia</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 07 Dec 2023 03:29:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>圭亚那加强安全，与美国合作保卫土地免受委内瑞拉侵害</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-06/guyana-boosts-security-engages-us-to-defend-land-from-venezuela</link>
      <description><![CDATA[圭亚那表示，正在加强安全措施，并与美国军队合作，帮助其保护石油资源丰富的埃塞奎博地区，并称委内瑞拉打算在该地区发放石油勘探许可证，这是对其领土完整的威胁。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-06/guyana-boosts-security-engages-us-to-defend-land-from-venezuela</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Dec 2023 14:16:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>意大利告诉中国它将退出“一带一路”投资协定</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-06/italy-notified-china-it-will-exit-belt-and-road-pact-radiocor</link>
      <description><![CDATA[意大利总理乔治亚·梅洛尼(Giorgia Meloni)领导的政府正式向中国表示将退出“一带一路”倡议，这对北京扩大大规模投资计划的雄心造成了新的打击。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-06/italy-notified-china-it-will-exit-belt-and-road-pact-radiocor</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Dec 2023 11:54:00 GMT</pubDate>
